<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.6">
<l>irunila maṉṉar tammai yirunālu meṭṭu morunālu moṉṟu muṭaṉē</l>
<l>cerunuta lūṭu pōki yavarāvi maṅka maḻuvāḷil veṉṟa tiṟalōṉ</l>
<l>perunila maṅkai maṉṉar malarmaṅkai nātar pulamaṅkai kēḷvar pukaḻcēr</l>
<l>perunila muṇṭu miḻnta peruvāya rāki yavarnammai yāḷvar peritē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That valiant warrior who, charging through the forefront of battle twice four,</l>
<l rend="indent">then eight, and four and one [times] all together</l>
<l>Conquered with an axe the kings of this vast land so their lives were ruined,</l>
<l>The king of the lady of the great earth, lord of the lady of the blossom,</l>
<l rend="indent">the beloved of the bashful lady,</l>
<l>Becoming the famed one whose great mouth consumed the great earth</l>
<l rend="indent">and expelled it, he rules us completely.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
